<h2>LIMS Developer's Manual - Database Monitor<br>
</h2>
<h3><span style="font-weight: bold;">Overview</span></h3>
<ul>
  <li>The bin/DB_monitor.pl script provides several database space
usage monitoring functionalities.<br>
  </li>
</ul>
<h3>Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Functionalities provided:</li>
  <ul>
    <li>For a user-specified list of hosts and databases:</li>
    <ul>
      <li>Report space usage</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Detail mode - report space usage for tables as well as
total usage of the database<br>
        </li>
        <li>Summary mode - only report total usage of the database</li>
        <li>Log mode - logs space usage information to a log file (this
log file is automatically written by the script in XML format)</li>
        <li>View mode - view space usage statistics over time based on
information stored in the XML log file</li>
      </ul>
    </ul>
  </ul>
  <li>Right now this script is run as a cron job under aldente@seqdb01.<br>
  </li>
</ul>
</span>
